function upGrade()

  local n, i  local m = 1  local k = string.char(44)
  for i = 1, 4 do  n = string.find(s, k, m)  m = n+1  end
  if string.sub(s, n+2, n+2) != k then
    local e = string.char(10)  local t  local g = ""  n = string.find(s, e)
    while string.len(s) > 6 do
      t = string.sub(s, 1, n)  s = string.sub(s, n+1)  m = 1
      for i = 1, 4 do  n = string.find(t, k, m)  m = n+1  end
      t = string.sub(t, 1, n).."1"..k..string.sub(t, n+1)  g = g..t  n = string.find(s, e)
    end  aBag.setLuaScript(g..s)
  end
end

function findBags()
    mBag = nil  aBag = nil wBase = nil
    local aoj = {}  aoj = getAllObjects()  local g, s, n  n = 1  s = ""  g = aoj[1]
    while g do
      if g.getDescription() == "_OW_mBaG" then  if mBag then mBag = "e" else mBag = g end  end
      if string.sub(g.getDescription(), 1, 8) == "_OW_aBaG" then  if aBag then aBag = "e" else aBag = g end  end
      if g.getName() == "_OW_wBase" then wBase = g end
      n = n+1  g = aoj[n]
    end
    if not mBag then broadcastToAll("Missing Zone Object Bag.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  newMBag()  return false  end
    if not aBag then broadcastToAll("Missing Base Token Bag.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  newABag()  return false  end
    if mBag == "e" or aBag == "e" then broadcastToAll("Bag Count Error.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  return false  end
    if not wBase then s = s.." No Map View Token." end
    if mBag.getName() == "Same_Name_Here" or aBag.getName() == "Same_Name_Here" then s = s.." ReName Your Bags." end
    if mBag.getName() != aBag.getName() then s = s.." Unmatched Bag Names." end
    if s != "" then  broadcastToAll(s, {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  return false
      else return true end
end

      if wBase.getCustomObject().image == aBase.getCustomObject().image then  wBase.setColorTint(aBase.getColorTint())  f = f+2  end
    end
    if f == 0 or f == 2 then vBase.setColorTint(sBase.getColorTint()) end  if f < 2 then wBase.setColorTint(sBase.getColorTint()) end
    if wpx == nil or wpx == wBase.getDescription() then wBase.call("setLinks") end
    if nl then wBase.call("makeLink") end

    for i = 0, string.len(ss)/6-1 do  g = string.sub(ss, i*6+1, i*6+6)
      if not getObjectFromGUID(g) then ss = string.sub(ss, 1, i*6)..string.sub(ss, i*6+7) end
    end  if ss == "" then do return  end  end
    cbc = 0  z2 = z2 + 1  if z2/10 == math.modf(z2/10) then broadcastToAll("Pass"..(z2/10).."...", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  end

function parceData(a)
  local h = string.char(45)  local k = string.char(44)  local e = string.char(10)  local s = aBag.getLuaScript()
  local g = a[1] local n = string.find(s, k, string.find(s, h..g..k))  local m = n
  if not n then broadcastToAll("Missing Base.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  do return  end  end
  local d = {}  local i
  for i = 1, 4 do  n = string.find(s, k, m+1)  d[i] = string.sub(s, m+1, n-1)  m = n  end
  n = string.find(s, e, m+1)  d[5] = string.sub(s, m+1, n-1)  if d[5] == nil then d[5] = "" end
  d[4] = tonumber(d[4])  if d[4] == 0 then d[4] = 8 elseif d[4] == 1 or d[4] == 2 then d[4] = nil end  --[[ convert old data --]]
  if wpx and wpx != g then d[4] = nil end  return string.gsub(d[1], ";", ","), tonumber(d[2]), tonumber(d[3]), d[4], d[5]
end

function doBuild()
    local v = {}  v = iBag.getObjects()
    prs = aBase.getLuaScript()

    prs = string.gsub(prs, string.char(10), string.char(44))
    local x, y, z  local ct = 1  local n  ss = ""  zz = 0
    while v[ct] do
        n = string.find(prs, "-"..v[ct].guid..",")
        if n then
            local t = {}  t.guid = v[ct].guid  t.position = {0, -15, 0}  n = n+8  zz = zz+1
            x, n = snipIt({n})  y, n = snipIt({n})  z, n = snipIt({n})  t.position = {x-70, y+70, z-70}
            x, n = snipIt({n})  y, n = snipIt({n})  z, n = snipIt({n})  t.rotation = {x, y, z}
            t.callback = "setStage"  t.callback_owner = self  iBag.takeObject(t)
        end  ct = ct + 1
    end
end
function snipIt(a)  local e = string.find(prs, string.char(44), a[1])  return string.sub(prs, a[1], e-1), e+1  end
function setStage(a)
    local x, y, z  a.resting = true  a.lock()  local n = string.find(prs, "-"..a.guid..",")+8  zz = zz-1
    y, n = snipIt({n})  z, n = snipIt({n})  x, n = snipIt({n})  a.setPosition({y, z, x})
    y, n = snipIt({n})  z, n = snipIt({n})  x, n = snipIt({n})  a.setRotation({y, z, x})
    ss = ss..(a.guid)  if zz == 0 then cbOn({"popSetQ"})  end
end
function popSetQ()  zz = zz+1  if zz > 5 then zz = 0  z2 = 0  cbOff()  cbOn({"popSet"})  end  end
function popSet()
    if ss == "" then cbOff()  popSetZ()  do return  end  end
    local x, y, z, a, b, c, n, g, p, r
    g = string.sub(ss, 1, 6)  n = string.find(prs, "-"..g..",")+8
    if not getObjectFromGUID(g) then ss = string.sub(ss, 7)  print("Missing")  do return  end  end
    y, n = snipIt({n})  z, n = snipIt({n})  x, n = snipIt({n})  p = getObjectFromGUID(g).getPosition()
    a, n = snipIt({n})  b, n = snipIt({n})  c, n = snipIt({n})  r = getObjectFromGUID(g).getRotation()
    if getObjectFromGUID(g).resting then
        if math.abs(p[1]-y) < 0.0005 and math.abs(p[2]-z) < 0.0005 and math.abs(p[3]-x) < 0.0005 and
            math.abs(r[1]-a) < 0.0005 and math.abs(r[2]-b) < 0.0005 and math.abs(r[3]-c) < 0.0005 then
            z2 = z2+1  if z2 > 9 then zz = 0 end
        else zz = zz+1
            getObjectFromGUID(g).setRotation({a, b, c})  getObjectFromGUID(g).setPosition({y, z, x})  getObjectFromGUID(g).resting = true
        end
    else getObjectFromGUID(g).resting = true  zz = zz+1
    end
    if zz > 21 then getObjectFromGUID(g).resting = true  print("Failed Alignment")  zz = 0  end
    if zz == 0 then ss = string.sub(ss, 7)  z2 = 0  end
end
function popSetZ()  prs = ""  cbOn({"pickLocks"})  end
function pickLocks()
    if cbc < 10 then do return  end  end  cbOff()
    local s = aBase.getLuaScript() local n = 0

        local g = string.sub(s, n+3, n+8)  n = string.find(s, string.char(10), n+3)
        if getObjectFromGUID(g) and string.sub(s, n-1, n-1) == "0" then getObjectFromGUID(g).unlock() end
    end

ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
--44dd06
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end

-- ^^^  DO NOT ALTER OR REMOVE THESE LINES ABOVE  ^^^

o = nil

function onCollisionEnter(a)
    if not Global.getVar("oWisOn") or o == a.collision_object or o == 1 then do return  end  end
    o = a.collision_object  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    local g = string.sub(o.getName(), 1, 4)  if g == "SET_" then g = "OWx_" end
    local i = "https://sites.google.com/site/rolesystemssky/x.png"
    if self.getDescription() == "" and g == "SBx_" and o.name == "Custom_Token" then newBase()
      elseif self.getDescription() == "" and g == "OWx_" and o.name == "Bag" then doImport()
      elseif self.getDescription() != "" and o.getCustomObject().image == i then addLink()
      else if g == "SBx_" or g == "OWx_" then broadcastToAll("!! clear hub to import !!", {0.7, 0.7, 0.7}) end
        local v = ow.getVar("vBase")  local s = v.getLuaScript()  local n = string.len(s)
        while string.sub(s, n) != "@" do  s = string.sub(s, 1, n-1)  n = n-1  end
        g = o.guid  local n = string.find(s, g)  local b = ""  local q = "DO NOT PACK: "  if g then b = " ("..g..")" end
        if n then  q = "WILL PACK: "  s = string.sub(s, 1, n-1)..string.sub(s, n+7)  else  s = s..g.."@"  end
        v.setLuaScript(s)  broadcastToAll(q..a.collision_object.name..b, {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})
    end  ow.call("cbOn", {"popWB"})
end

function newBase()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))  local s = ow.getVar("aBag").getLuaScript()
  if string.find(s, "-"..o.guid ..",") then broadcastToAll("Duplicate GUID.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})
    else ow.call("putBase", {o.guid}) end
end

function doImport()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
  if string.sub(o.getName(), 1, 4) == "SET_" then
    o.setDescription("")  local v = {}  v = o.getObjects()  local n = 1
    while v[n] do
      if string.sub(v[n].name, 1, 4) == "SBx_" then
        ow.setVar("cbp", "i_"..o.guid)  o.setDescription(v[n].guid)  break
      end n = n+1
    end
    if o.getDescription() == "" then print("Sky Box Import Failed.")  do return end  end
  end
  broadcastToAll("Importing Art...", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  local t = {}  t.position = {-10, -45, 0}
  t.guid = o.getDescription()  t.callback = "preImport"  t.callback_owner = ow  o.takeObject(t)
end

function addLink()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
  if ow.call("isPVw") then  o.destruct()  do return end  end
  if o.getDescription() == self.getDescription() then
    o.destruct()  broadcastToAll("Link to Self.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  do return end  end
  local p = self.getPosition()  local h = 4.8  local v = 8.5  local r1 = ow.getVar("r1")  local r3 = ow.getVar("r3")
  local y = math.modf((o.getVar("l1")-p[1]+v/2)*100/v)  if y < 0 then y = 0 elseif y > 99 then y = 99 end
  local x = math.modf((o.getVar("l3")-p[3]+h/2)*100/h)  if x < 0 then x = 0 elseif x > 99 then x = 99 end
  if r1 == 180 then x = 99 - x end  if r3 == 180 then y = 99 - y end
  y = string.sub("0"..y, string.len(y))  x = string.sub("0"..x, string.len(x))
  ow.setVar("lnk", ow.getVar("lnk")..x..y.."@"..o.getDescription()..",")  o.destruct()  ow.call("jotBase")  setLinks()
end

function setLinks()
    self.clearButtons()  if self.getDescription() == "" then do return  end  end
    ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    local r1 = ow.getVar("r1")  local r3 = ow.getVar("r3")  local t = ow.getVar("lnk")
    local i  local h = 2.63  local v = 4.65  local r = 1  if r1 + r3 == 180 then r = -1 end
    local btn = {}  btn.function_owner = self  btn.label = " + "  btn.font_size = 150
    btn.rotation = {0, 45, 0}  btn.width = 100  btn.height = 100
    for i = 0, string.len(t)/12-1 do
        local n = i*12+1  local x = tonumber(string.sub(t, n, n+1))*h/100 - (h/2-0.016)
        local y = (v/2-0.018) - tonumber(string.sub(t, n+2, n+3))*v/100
        btn.click_function = "btnLink"..i  btn.position = {y, 0.055*r, x}  self.createButton(btn)
    end
end

function makeLink()
    local r2 = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale")).getVar("r2")  local x = self.getPosition()
    x[1] = x[1]-(5.5 * r2)  x[2]=x[2]+2.5  local p = {}  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {x[1], x[2], x[3]}
    p.rotation = {0, 90, 0}  p.scale = {0.1, 0.1, 0.1}  p.callback = "cbMLink"  p.callback_owner = self
    local o = spawnObject(p)  local i = {}  i.thickness = 0.01    i.image = "https://sites.google.com/site/rolesystemssky/x.png"  o.setCustomObject(i)end  function cbMLink(a)
    local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))  a.setDescription(ow.getVar("nl"))
    local bn = ow.call("parceData", {ow.getVar("nl")})  a.setName(bn)  ow.setVar("nl", nil)
    local s = self.getLuaScript()  s = string.sub(s, 6, string.find(s, "oW_4TT")-4)  a.setLuaScript(s)
end

function getLink(a)
    local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    if ow.getVar("cb[1]") then do return  end  end
    if ow.getVar("ef") then  ow.call("btnEdit")  do return end  end
    local l =  string.sub(ow.getVar("lnk"), a[1]*12+6, a[1]*12+11)  local bn = ow.call("parceData", {l})
    if bn != ow.getVar("mTxt").TextTool.getValue() then ow.call("showTxt", {bn, 1}) ow.setVar("ub", l)  ow.call("setBtn")
    else ow.call("getBase", {l}) end
end

ObjectStates.LuaScript:
--44dd06
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end


--tt

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end

Direct Fire && InDirectFire

If atleast Pinned - stay down

--[[iFtIeCW@Kxtgl5J@QWTUGhF@Iu4Yj5L@lBQ5rPa@MUOspF5@FCGgbhl@2AdgCyh@QNzSmo8@J886Ao1@vnlSpDg@D6Rr5pJ@
HY7bpco@Sc29wpI@kK5JASR@gawZh1f@ZdGWKAl@A1jdqsd@U5fk8Xx@7u0I7K5@RbZLh8T@q1eLKiL@wwoH99S@1DUlI5C@
i2R1CXc@rvWNRjO@mwbme0V@OKa5W9m@136Skso@FwoOInf@tcMp4tW@4x3rf6y@VfN36bO@zgWC4lC@69N9C3L@B8lPpqC@
DB4Y7aw@lB3iiKx@q6JQPsr@Q8yyTHj@ZDeqOMm@S3Cbu15@RI5fVVf@LXsW4eW@U2eDgV7@iYK2Iwd@2p0zkzx@Mo9aTzW@
88RmW0J@3MVGHf9@nTNSybB@feqit91@rxLdsyw@qkTxMQ8@FNBY72r@zYL3zEy@fCites6@oFLCpAg@SGCNMpe@HlmfEmA@
4sEWmTC@lYA1TyZ@tS9nN8t@kqDp87R@YveUEiY@lZd06tc@ELboN3M@A1vfo1G@wtqxQvN@xsO6GEe@aQmtmhU@kNEol1J@ --EnD]]

rz = ""  art = nil

function onLoad()
  onDestroy()
  local btn = {}  btn.function_owner = self  btn.width = 400  btn.height = 20
  btn.click_function = "btnClr"  btn.position = {-0.25, -0.05, -1.27}  self.createButton(btn)
  btn.click_function = "btnRez"  btn.position = {0.5, -0.05, -1.27}  self.createButton(btn)
  btn.click_function = "btnLong"  btn.position = {1.25, -0.05, -1.27}  self.createButton(btn)
  btn.click_function = "btnShort"  btn.position = {2, -0.05, -1.27}  self.createButton(btn)
  btn.click_function = "btnArt"  btn.position = {0, -0.05, 0.03}  btn.width = 2290  btn.height = 1150  self.createButton(btn)
end

function btnClr()  onDestroy()  end

function btnLong()
  if getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")) then
    local r = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).getRotation()
    getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).setRotation({r[1], r[2], r[3]+180})
  end
end

function btnShort()
  if getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")) then
    local r = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).getRotation()
    getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).setRotation({r[1]+180, r[2], r[3]})
  end
end

function btnRez()  local g = "Use HiRez Art."
  if rz == "" then  rz = "r"  g = "Use LowRez Art."  else  rz = ""  end  broadcastToAll(g, {0.7, 0.7, 0.7})  doArt()
end

function btnArt(d, c)  local i = self.getScale().x
  if i < 1 then self.setScale({1, 1, 1}) elseif i > 3 then self.setScale({3, 1, 3}) end
  if i != self.getScale().x then do return end  end
  local x = Player[c].getPointerPosition().x - self.getPosition().x
  local z = Player[c].getPointerPosition().z - self.getPosition().z
  local n = math.sqrt(x^2 + z^2)  local d = math.deg(math.atan(x/z))
  if z < 0 then d = 180+d elseif x < 0 then d = 360+d end
  d = d + 90 - self.getRotation().y  x = math.sin(math.rad(d)) * n  z = x / math.tan(math.rad(d))
  x = math.modf(3+(x/i/0.398)) z = math.modf(6+(z/(i/0.5854)/0.23))
  local s = self.getLuaScript()  s = string.sub(s, 5, string.find(s, "-EnD")-3)
  n = x*(8*12+2) + z*8 + 1  art = string.sub(s, n, n+6)  doArt()
end

function doArt()  if not art then do return end  end
  if not makeView() then
    local w = {}  w.image = "http://i.imgur.com/"..art..rz..".jpg"
    getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).setCustomObject(w)
    getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).reload()
  end
end

function makeView()
  if not getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")) then
    local p = {}  local i = {}  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, 0.91, 0}  p.rotation = {0, 0, 0}
    p.callback = "cbMView"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p)
    i.thickness = 0.1  i.image = "https://sites.google.com/site/rolesystemssky/bm_wood.jpg"
    o.setCustomObject(i)  return true
  end
end

function cbMView(a)  Global.setVar("bmR4meTT", a.guid)
  local s = "function onLoad()  if not Global.getVar('bmR4meTT') then self.destruct() end  end"
  a.setLuaScript(s)  a.lock()  a.interactable = false  a.setScale({18.57, 1, 17.6})
end

function onDestroy()
  if getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")) then
    getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("bmR4meTT")).destruct()
  end
end


--tt

ContainedObjects.Name: BlockSquare
ContainedObjects.Description:
Initiative swaps to another player if current phasing player fail

Failed actions are:
Moving squad is suppressed or killed by reactive file
Fail to suppress or kill target during phasing Direct Fire (not InDirect)
Fail to Detect enemy Through Recon by Fire
Fail to Rally
Losing in Close Combat
Hung up in Barbed Wire or Suppressed by Mines
Phasing player "passing"

ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
--559f24
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end


--tt

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model
ContainedObjects.Description:
Regular

Can't Fire
Can't CQB
Can control fire only if remains stationary for entire initiative 
&& Not Pinned/Suppressed
&& Have LOS on target

Can target any Squads or CC
PL / FO Proximity rule
Only one Artillery Fire per initiative; 
If miss - no loss of Initiatiive
Can't target Enemy PL or FO
Unless no other Squads around

Hit the Dirt: No
ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
--2b2867
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end


--tt

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model
ContainedObjects.Description:
Cross like object
No Protection && No Block LOS

5-6 Green
4-6 Regular
3-6 Veterans

IF success && not pin by Reactive fire 
THEN cross ELSE loose Initiative
Can be attacked by all fire && Close Combat WHILE in Barbed Wire 

Can be cleared by:
Engineer - one separate initiative
Armor - Destroy on contact
APC/Tracked - Destroy && Stop
Barrage fire - 4 Hits in total

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model
ContainedObjects.Description:
Regular

Can't Fire
Can't CQB
Can control fire only if remains stationary for entire initiative 
&& Not Pinned/Suppressed
&& Have LOS on target

Can target any Squads or CC
PL / FO Proximity rule
Only one Artillery Fire per initiative; 
If miss - no loss of Initiatiive
Can't target Enemy PL or FO
Unless no other Squads around

Hit the Dirt: No
ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
--2b2867
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)

ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model
ContainedObjects.Description:
Regular

Fire: 4 d6
Arc of Fire: 45 Front
Hit the Dirt: No

CQB Modifier: -2
ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
--614466
tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end


--tt

tm = os.clock()  ps = 0  n = {}

function onLoad()  self.auto_raise = false  end

function onPickUp()  tm = os.clock()  onDestroy()  Player[self.held_by_color].lift_height = 0  end

function onDrop()
  if ps != 2 and os.clock()-tm < 0.26 then ps = ps+1
    if ps == 1 then makePS("pin") else makePS("sup") end
  else  ps = 0  end
end

function onCollisionEnter()  n = self.getPosition()  end

function makePS(a)
  local p = {}  local i = {}
  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {0, -33, 0}  p.rotation = {90, self.getRotation().y + 90, 90}
  p.callback = "cbMake"  p.callback_owner = self  local o = spawnObject(p) i.merge_distance = 5
  i.thickness = 0.16  i.image = "cf.tacticalshift.ru/3d/cfx_"..a..".png"  o.setCustomObject(i)
end
function cbMake(a)
  a.lock()  a.setScale({0.3, 1, 0.3})  putGUID(a.guid)  a.setPosition({n[1], n[2]+4, n[3]})
  local g  if ps == 1 then g = "ffa18c" else g = "ecd4bb" end
  a.setName(getObjectFromGUID(g).getName())  a.setDescription(getObjectFromGUID(g).getDescription())
end

function getGUID()  return(string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 3, 8))  end
function putGUID(a)  self.setLuaScript("--"..a..string.sub(self.getLuaScript(), 9))  end
function onDestroy()  if getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()) then getObjectFromGUID(getGUID()).destruct() end  end

o = nil

function onCollisionEnter(a)
    if not Global.getVar("oWisOn") or o == a.collision_object or o == 1 then do return  end  end
    o = a.collision_object  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    local g = string.sub(o.getName(), 1, 4)  if g == "SET_" then g = "OWx_" end
    local i = "https://sites.google.com/site/rolesystemssky/x.png"
    if self.getDescription() == "" and g == "SBx_" and o.name == "Custom_Token" then newBase()
      elseif self.getDescription() == "" and g == "OWx_" and o.name == "Bag" then doImport()
      elseif self.getDescription() != "" and o.getCustomObject().image == i then addLink()
      else if g == "SBx_" or g == "OWx_" then broadcastToAll("!! clear hub to import !!", {0.7, 0.7, 0.7}) end
        local v = ow.getVar("vBase")  local s = v.getLuaScript()  local n = string.len(s)
        while string.sub(s, n) != "@" do  s = string.sub(s, 1, n-1)  n = n-1  end
        g = o.guid  local n = string.find(s, g)  local b = ""  local q = "DO NOT PACK: "  if g then b = " ("..g..")" end
        if n then  q = "WILL PACK: "  s = string.sub(s, 1, n-1)..string.sub(s, n+7)  else  s = s..g.."@"  end
        v.setLuaScript(s)  broadcastToAll(q..a.collision_object.name..b, {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})
    end  ow.call("cbOn", {"popWB"})
end

function newBase()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))  local s = ow.getVar("aBag").getLuaScript()
  if string.find(s, "-"..o.guid ..",") then broadcastToAll("Duplicate GUID.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})
    else ow.call("putBase", {o.guid}) end
end

function doImport()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
  if string.sub(o.getName(), 1, 4) == "SET_" then
    o.setDescription("")  local v = {}  v = o.getObjects()  local n = 1
    while v[n] do
      if string.sub(v[n].name, 1, 4) == "SBx_" then
        ow.setVar("cbp", "i_"..o.guid)  o.setDescription(v[n].guid)  break
      end n = n+1
    end
    if o.getDescription() == "" then print("Sky Box Import Failed.")  do return end  end
  end
  broadcastToAll("Importing Art...", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  local t = {}  t.position = {-10, -45, 0}
  t.guid = o.getDescription()  t.callback = "preImport"  t.callback_owner = ow  o.takeObject(t)
end

function addLink()
  local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
  if ow.call("isPVw") then  o.destruct()  do return end  end
  if o.getDescription() == self.getDescription() then
    o.destruct()  broadcastToAll("Link to Self.", {0.943, 0.745, 0.14})  do return end  end
  local p = self.getPosition()  local h = 4.8  local v = 8.5  local r1 = ow.getVar("r1")  local r3 = ow.getVar("r3")
  local y = math.modf((o.getVar("l1")-p[1]+v/2)*100/v)  if y < 0 then y = 0 elseif y > 99 then y = 99 end
  local x = math.modf((o.getVar("l3")-p[3]+h/2)*100/h)  if x < 0 then x = 0 elseif x > 99 then x = 99 end
  if r1 == 180 then x = 99 - x end  if r3 == 180 then y = 99 - y end
  y = string.sub("0"..y, string.len(y))  x = string.sub("0"..x, string.len(x))
  ow.setVar("lnk", ow.getVar("lnk")..x..y.."@"..o.getDescription()..",")  o.destruct()  ow.call("jotBase")  setLinks()
end

function setLinks()
    self.clearButtons()  if self.getDescription() == "" then do return  end  end
    ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    local r1 = ow.getVar("r1")  local r3 = ow.getVar("r3")  local t = ow.getVar("lnk")
    local i  local h = 2.63  local v = 4.65  local r = 1  if r1 + r3 == 180 then r = -1 end
    local btn = {}  btn.function_owner = self  btn.label = " + "  btn.font_size = 150
    btn.rotation = {0, 45, 0}  btn.width = 100  btn.height = 100
    for i = 0, string.len(t)/12-1 do
        local n = i*12+1  local x = tonumber(string.sub(t, n, n+1))*h/100 - (h/2-0.016)
        local y = (v/2-0.018) - tonumber(string.sub(t, n+2, n+3))*v/100
        btn.click_function = "btnLink"..i  btn.position = {y, 0.055*r, x}  self.createButton(btn)
    end
end

function makeLink()
    local r2 = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale")).getVar("r2")  local x = self.getPosition()
    x[1] = x[1]-(5.5 * r2)  x[2]=x[2]+2.5  local p = {}  p.type = "Custom_Token"  p.position = {x[1], x[2], x[3]}
    p.rotation = {0, 90, 0}  p.scale = {0.1, 0.1, 0.1}  p.callback = "cbMLink"  p.callback_owner = self
    local o = spawnObject(p)  local i = {}  i.thickness = 0.01    i.image = "https://sites.google.com/site/rolesystemssky/x.png"  o.setCustomObject(i)end  function cbMLink(a)
    local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))  a.setDescription(ow.getVar("nl"))
    local bn = ow.call("parceData", {ow.getVar("nl")})  a.setName(bn)  ow.setVar("nl", nil)
    local s = self.getLuaScript()  s = string.sub(s, 6, string.find(s, "oW_4TT")-4)  a.setLuaScript(s)
end

function getLink(a)
    local ow = getObjectFromGUID(Global.getVar("oW4TTale"))
    if ow.getVar("cb[1]") then do return  end  end
    if ow.getVar("ef") then  ow.call("btnEdit")  do return end  end
    local l =  string.sub(ow.getVar("lnk"), a[1]*12+6, a[1]*12+11)  local bn = ow.call("parceData", {l})
    if bn != ow.getVar("mTxt").TextTool.getValue() then ow.call("showTxt", {bn, 1}) ow.setVar("ub", l)  ow.call("setBtn")
    else ow.call("getBase", {l}) end
end

0.title: Rules
0.body:
[u][b]REVERSI:[/b][/u]

[b]GAME OBJECTIVE:[/b]
Players take turns placing disks on the board with their assigned color facing up. During a play, any disks of the opponent's color that are in a straight line and bounded by the disk just placed and another disk of the current player's color are turned over to the current player's color.
The object of the game is to have the majority of disks turned to display your color when the last playable empty square is filled.

[b]GAMEPLAY:[/b]
True Reversi starts with an empty board, and the first two moves by each player are in the four central squares of the board. The players place their disks alternately with their color facing up and no captures are made.
The dark player makes the first move.  Dark must place a piece with the dark side up on the board, in such a position that there exists at least one straight (horizontal, vertical, or diagonal) occupied line between the new piece and another dark piece, with one or more contiguous light pieces between them.
After placing the piece, dark turns over (flips) all light pieces lying on a straight line between the new piece and any anchoring dark pieces. All reversed pieces now show the dark side, and dark can use them in later moves—unless light has reversed them back in the meantime. In other words, a valid move is one where at least one piece is reversed.
The light player now plays. This player operates under the same Notepad, with the roles reversed: light lays down a light piece, causing a dark piece to flip. Players keep alternating their turns.

[b]WINNING THE GAME:[/b]
If one player cannot make a valid move, play passes back to the other player. When neither player can move, the game ends. This occurs when the grid has filled up, or when one player has no more pieces on the board, or when neither player can legally place a piece in any of the remaining squares. The player with the most pieces on the board at the end of the game wins.

Please note that these Notepad are one in many out there, but this is a good starting point for one way to play the game. If you’d like to find other ways to play, you can search online. [b]Have fun![/b]
